INTRODUCTION                                                       *wort-intro*

Personal Neovim configuration using native features (vim.pack, vim.lsp) with
minimal external dependencies. Philosophy: explicit, predictable, portable -
missing tools skip gracefully rather than error.

Structure~

  init.lua            Entry point, loads modules in order
  lua/core/           Core settings (options, keymaps, autocmds)
  lua/pack.lua        Plugin declarations for vim.pack
  lua/plugins/        Individual plugin configurations
  lua/lsp/            LSP configuration and server definitions
  lua/local.lua       Machine-specific overrides (gitignored)

